en_7811381_0	Six UPFA Eastern Provincial Councillors, including Former Ministers Wimalaweera Dissanayake, Uduma Lebbe, M.L.A. Ameer, W.D. Weerasinghe, D.M. Jayasena and Jayantha Wijesekara have withdrawn support to SLMC Chief Minister Hafeez Nazir Ahmed.
en_7811381_1	They informed the governor via affidavits that affidavits were provided by by the councilors on a prior occasion pledging their support to the CM will be withdrawn.
en_7811381_2	Governor of the Eastern Province, Austin Fernando, has accepted the affidavits.
